Date: Mon, 30 Mar 2026 07:19:34 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 17/34] =?UTF-8?q?refactor:=20simplify=20BUILD=20files=20?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=E2=80=94=20exports=5Ffiles=20moved=20into=20orfs=5Fdesign()?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- Design BUILD files reduced from 5 lines to 3 (load + orfs_design(designs = DESIGNS, mock_openroad = "@bazel-orfs//mock/openroad/src/bin:openroad"))
- orfs_design(designs = DESIGNS, mock_openroad = "@bazel-orfs//mock/openroad/src/bin:openroad") now calls native.exports_files(glob(['*'])) internally
- Auto-generated nested src BUILD files for referenced subdirectories
- 82 design BUILD files simplified, 39 src BUILD files auto-generated
- Disabled mempool_group (complex include dir dependencies)
- 51/51 tests pass across all 6 platforms

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
Signed-off-by: Øyvind Harboe <oyvind.harboe@zylin.com>
